WEBVTT

00:13:29.722 --> 00:13:33.283
that is causing us to track
anything of substance

00:13:33.307 --> 00:13:35.006
about the way the world is.

00:13:35.030 --> 00:13:38.125
We're not in touch with reality
when we're moralizing.

00:13:38.149 --> 00:13:40.006
We're just apes with preferences.

00:13:40.030 --> 00:13:41.891
And so these two things,

00:13:41.915 --> 00:13:43.704
the fact of moral diversity

00:13:43.728 --> 00:13:48.814
and the fact that much of our morality
is anchored to these evolved,

00:13:48.838 --> 00:13:51.194
apish tendencies,

00:13:51.218 --> 00:13:54.393
those two things have led
many, many smart people

00:13:54.417 --> 00:13:56.433
to believe that there's no there there,

00:13:56.457 --> 00:13:59.243
there's no truth
with respect to right and wrong.

00:13:59.267 --> 00:14:01.434
CA: I mean, by presenting
the ISIS case there,